Recipe for porridge

Ingredients:
1 cup oats
1 cup milk
1/2-1 cup of hot water
1/2 tsp salt
generous dash of cream
handful of chopped nuts and dried fruits (optional)

1) put oats, salt, milk, cream into a bowl and stir
2) add the water until your bowl is quite full (1-2cm below the rim)
3) microwave for 2 mins, then stit
4) microwave for a further 1min or until porridge starts to bubble up to the rim (watch it!)
5) stir in fruit and nuts
6) microwave for a further 1min or until porridge starts to bubble up to the rim (watch it!)
7) stir and leave to stand (1-2mins)
8) enjoy!
